casebody.data:
Rodney KEISTER, petitioner,
v.
Stuart BELL, in His Official Capacity as President of the University of Alabama, et al. No. 18-17. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 1, 2018.

*209Motion of Alliance Defending Freedom, et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eleventh Circuit denied.
